      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was [? director, ?] and we have been together in the army in the war time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So [? they ?] help me, what was a very unique thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Both my daughters started study at the university.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
